===Strategy===
* Can use a maximum of 1 [[Land Base Aerial Support]] squadron. No abyssal air raid.
* '''You need at least 5 range to reach the boss''' with your [[Land Base Aerial Support]].
* The standard land base loadout is 3 land-based bombers + 1 fighter for maximum damage output on the boss node.
*Requires sinking the flagship at the boss node '''5 TIMES''' to deplete the gauge and clear the map.
*Maximum 2 [[BB]] and/or 2 [[CV]]/[[CVL]] allowed to sortie.
*The boss node has 3-5 [[Installation Type|land based]] targets, {{ShipLink|Isolated Island Princess}} and {{ShipLink|Supply Depot Princess}}, accompanied by 2-3 {{ShipLink|Artillery Imp}}s.
**WG42, Type 3 Shells and AP shells will help increase damage on these enemies.
*On the last kill boss and pre-boss nodes switches to stronger patterns as noted with <span style="color:red">'''(Final)'''</span> in the patterns table below.

